<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <title>DCHEQS Conversion Accounts Cashline</title>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <style type="text/css">
        @page {
            size: A4;
            font-family: EmbCenturyGothic;
            margin-left: 50px;
            margin-right: 50px;
            margin-top: 25mm;
            @top-left {
                content: element(header);
            }
        }

        body {
            font-family: EmbCenturyGothic;
            font-size: 10pt;
            text-align: justify;
        }

        header {
            text-align: left;
            position: running(header);
            width: 677px;
            margin-left: 7.5px;
        }

        .first-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }

        .first-table td {
            padding-left: 6px;
            vertical-align: top;
        }

        .firstColWidth {
            width: 35%;
        }

        .secondColWidth {
            width: 5%;
            text-align: center;
            font-family: EmbCenturyGothicBold;
            font-weight: normal;
        }

        .second-table-header {
            background-color: #b0b0b0;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .second-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }

        .second-table td {
            padding-left: 6px;
            vertical-align: top;
            border: 1px solid;

        }
        
        #second-table-1st-row-width{
            width: 7%;
        }
        #second-table-2nd-row-width{
            width: 28%;
        }   
        #second-table-3rd-row-width{
            width: 30%;
        }
        #second-table-4th-row-width{
            width: 35%;
        }

        .leftPadding {
            padding-left: 6px;
        }

        .fontBold {
            font-family: EmbCenturyGothicBold;
            font-weight: normal;
        }
        .fontItalicBold{
            font-family: EmbCenturyGothicItalicBold; 
            font-weight: normal;
        }

        .break {
            word-wrap: break-word;
            white-space: normal;
            overflow-wrap: break-word;
        }

        .page-break {
            page-break-before: always;
        }

        .alignTextCenter {
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body style="margin-top: 0px;">
    <header style="font-size: 8pt;margin-top: 50px;">
        <div>
            <img src="${contextVariables.bankIslamLogo!}" alt="bank_islam_logo" style="vertical-align: middle; margin-left: 5px; width:216px; height:50px;display: inline-block "/>
            
            <p style="
            margin-left: 10px;
            display: inline-block;
            vertical-align: middle;
            line-height: 1.1;
          ">
                Jika tidak sampai, sila kembalikan kepada :-<br />
                <span style="white-space: nowrap">
                    P.O. Box 12176, 50724 Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia
                </span>
            </p>
        </div>
        <div>
            <p style="
            margin-top: 5px;
            margin-left: 5px;
            line-height: 1.2;
          ">
                SULIT &amp; PERSENDIRIAN<br />
                Untuk dibuka oleh Penerima sahaja
            </p>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main>
        <p class="leftPadding fontBold" style="padding-top: 40px;">PRIVATE &amp; CONFIDENTIAL</p>
        <table class="first-table">
            <tr>
                <td class="firstColWidth">Date</td>
                <td class="secondColWidth">:</td>
                <td class="break">1.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td class="firstColWidth">Customer’s Name</td>
                <td class="secondColWidth">:</td>
                <td class="break">2.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td class="firstColWidth">Address</td>
                <td class="secondColWidth">:</td>
                <td class="break">3.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td class="firstColWidth">Current Account No.</td>
                <td class="secondColWidth">:</td>
                <td class="break">4.</td>
            </tr>
        </table>
        <div class="leftPadding">
            <p>Assalamualaikum / Greetings,</p>
            <p>Y.Bhg. Dato’ Sri / Datin Sri / Dato’ / Datuk / Datin / Encik / Tuan/Puan,</p>
            <div class="fontBold">NOTIFICATION ON THE CONVERSION OF CUSTOMER’S CURRENT ACCOUNT WITH CASH LINE-I FACILITY
                TO ‘SPECIAL ACCOUNT’</div>
            <div style="border: 1px solid;"></div>
            <p>We refer to the above matter.</p>
            <p>Despite our reminders, you have failed, refused, and/or neglected to ensure sufficient funds in your
                account to pay the amount of the cheques issued. The details are as follows:- </p>
            <table class="second-table">
                <tr>
                    <td class="second-table-header alignTextCenter fontBold">No.</td>
                    <td class="second-table-header break fontBold">Cheque No.</td>
                    <td class="second-table-header fontBold">Amount</td>
                    <td class="second-table-header fontBold">Date of Dishonoured Cheques</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="alignTextCenter" id="second-table-1st-row-width">1</td>
                    <td id="second-table-2nd-row-width" class="break">5.</td>
                    <td id="second-table-3rd-row-width" class="break" >7.</td>
                    <td id="second-table-4th-row-width" class="break">6.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="alignTextCenter">2</td>
                    <td class="break">5.</td>
                    <td class="break">7.</td>
                    <td class="break">6.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="alignTextCenter">3</td>
                    <td class="break">5.</td>
                    <td class="break">7.</td>
                    <td class="break">6.</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
            <p>Accordingly, we write to inform you that the above mentioned account will be converted to <span
                    class="fontBold">“Special Account”</span> effective from 8.</p>
            <p>In view of the above, you are required to inform us the number of cheques issued but yet to be presented
                and return all unused cheques within <span class="fontBold">ten (10) working days</span> from the date
                of this letter, failing which, the Bank shall not be liable for any consequences thereof. </p>
            <p>Should you need further clarification, please contact the nearest Bank Islam branch. Your co-operation in
                this matter would be highly appreciated. Thank you. </p>
            <p>Yours faithfully,</p>
            <br />
            <div class="fontBold">BANK ISLAM MALAYSIA BERHAD</div>
            <div class="break">9.</div>
            <p>No signature required, system generated.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="page-break"></div>

        <p class="leftPadding fontBold" style="padding-top: 40px;">SULIT DAN PERSENDIRIAN</p>
        <table class="first-table">
            <tr>
                <td class="firstColWidth">Tarikh</td>
                <td class="secondColWidth">:</td>
                <td class="break">1.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td class="firstColWidth">Nama Pelanggan</td>
                <td class="secondColWidth">:</td>
                <td class="break">2.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td class="firstColWidth">Alamat</td>
                <td class="secondColWidth">:</td>
                <td class="break">3.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td class="firstColWidth">No. Akaun Semasa</td>
                <td class="secondColWidth">:</td>
                <td class="break">4.</td>
            </tr>
        </table>
        <div class="leftPadding">
            <p>Assalamualaikum / Salam Sejahtera,</p>
            <p>Y.Bhg. Dato’ Sri / Datin Sri / Dato’ / Datuk / Datin / Encik / Puan,</p>
            <div class="fontBold">PEMBERITAHUAN BERKENAAN PERNUKARAN STATUS AKAUN SEMASA PELANGGAN DENGAN KEMUDAHAN <span class="fontItalicBold">CASH LINE-i</span> KEPADA <span class="fontItalicBold">‘SPECIAL ACCOUNT’</span></div>
            <div style="border: 1px solid;"></div>
            <p>Merujuk kepada perkara di atas.</p>
            <p>Walaupun peringatan telah diberikan, anda telah gagal, enggan, dan/atau cuai untuk memastikan baki akaun anda mencukupi bagi membayar jumlah cek-cek yang telah dikeluarkan. Butir-butir adalah seperti berikut:- </p>
            <table class="second-table">
                <tr>
                    <td class="second-table-header alignTextCenter fontBold">No.</td>
                    <td class="second-table-header break fontBold">No. Cek</td>
                    <td class="second-table-header fontBold">Jumlah</td>
                    <td class="second-table-header fontBold">Tarikh Cek Tak Laku</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="alignTextCenter" id="second-table-1st-row-width">1</td>
                    <td id="second-table-2nd-row-width" class="break">5.</td>
                    <td id="second-table-3rd-row-width" class="break" >7.</td>
                    <td id="second-table-4th-row-width" class="break">6.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="alignTextCenter">2</td>
                    <td class="break">5.</td>
                    <td class="break">7.</td>
                    <td class="break">6.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="alignTextCenter">3</td>
                    <td class="break">5.</td>
                    <td class="break">7.</td>
                    <td class="break">6.</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
            <p>Oleh yang demikian, kami ingin memaklumkan bahawa status akaun semasa anda akan ditukarkan kepada <span class="fontBold">“Special Account”</span> berkuatkuasa 8.</p>
            <p>Disebabkan perkara di atas, anda diminta untuk memaklumkan jumlah cek-cek yang telah dikeluarkan tetapi masih belum dihantarserah dan mengembalikan kesemua cek yang tidak digunakan dalam tempoh <span class="fontBold">sepuluh (10) hari bekerja</span> daripada tarikh surat ini kepada kami, yang mana sekiranya gagal, pihak Bank tidak akan bertanggungjawab terhadap sebarang kegagalan penjelasan cek-cek yang dikeluarkan daripadanya.</p>
            <p>Untuk sebarang pertanyaan, sila hubungi cawangan Bank Islam yang terdekat. Kerjasama anda di dalam perkara ini amat kami hargai. Terima kasih.</p>
            <p>Yang benar,</p>
            <br />
            <div class="fontBold">BANK ISLAM MALAYSIA BERHAD</div>
            <div class="break">9.</div>
            <p>Ini adalah dokumen cetakan komputer, tiada tandatangan diperlukan.</p>
        </div>
    </main>
</body>
</html>